031200
031300     IF     ATTRIBUTE RESTARTED OF MYSELF  =  VALUE TRUE
031400            DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T434/DB : TERMINO ANORMAL"
031500            MOVE    997             TO      IA1
031600            PERFORM 200-E-ENV-ERRO  THRU    200-S-ENV-ERRO
031700            GO                      TO      000-S-MONITORA.
031800
031900
032000     PERFORM 010-E-INICIO           THRU    010-S-INICIO.
