037500                                             AREA-OUT.
037600
037700
037800     RECEIVE COMS-IN MESSAGE         INTO    AREA-IN.
037900
038000
038100     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       00 OR 89 OR 92 OR
038200                                             93 OR 97
038300             NEXT    SENTENCE
038400     ELSE
