038600             GO                      TO      030-S-PROCESSA
038700     ELSE
038800             PERFORM 250-E-ERRO-COMS THRU    250-S-ERRO-COMS
038900             GO                      TO      030-S-PROCESSA.
039000
039100     MOVE    COMS-IN-USERCODE        TO      USER-DESG.
