041000     ELSE
041100             MOVE    999             TO      IA1
041200             PERFORM 200-E-ENV-ERRO  THRU    200-S-ENV-ERRO.
041300
041400
041500     MOVE    COMS-IN-STATION         TO      COMS-OUT-DESTINATION.
041600     MOVE    AX-AGENDA-DESG          TO      COMS-OUT-AGENDA.
041700
041800     MOVE    1                       TO      COMS-OUT-COUNT.
041900     MOVE    0                       TO      COMS-OUT-STATUS.
042000
042100     IF      IA1                     =       ZEROS
042200             MOVE   ZEROS            TO      OUT-RETORNO
