053900*
054000 100-E-LOCK-NVPLAC.
054100*
054200
054300     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-NOTFOUND.
054400
054500
054600     LOCK    NOVAPLACSS6    AT
054700             NPL-CHASSI              =       IN-CHASSI
