056002*----------------------------------------------------------------*
056004*    SORTEAR VALOR
056006*----------------------------------------------------------------*
056008 120-E-SORTEAR.
056010
056012     MOVE    ZEROS               TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1).
056014
056016***  SE NECESSARIO INICIALIZAR O SEED
056018     IF  SEED                    EQUAL   0
056020         ACCEPT  SEED            FROM    TIME
056022     ELSE
056024         NEXT SENTENCE.
056026
056028***  EFETUAR O SORTEIO
056030     CALL "RANDOM OF GENERALSUPPORT"
056032         USING   SEED
056034         GIVING  RANDOM-RESULT.
056036
056038     MOVE    RANDOM-RESULT       TO      WS-RAND.
056040
056042***  MANTER A FAIXA MINIMA JUNTO COM AS EXISTENTES
056044     IF  AI1                     =      1
056046         COMPUTE AX-SORT-SUM = AX-SORT-MIN + WS-RAND-VALUE
056048
056050         IF  AX-SORT-SUM         >       9999
056052             MOVE WS-RAND-VALUE  TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1)
056054         ELSE
056056             MOVE AX-SORT-SUM    TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1)
056058     ELSE
056060         MOVE WS-RAND-VALUE      TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1).
056062
056064***  PROXIMO REGISTRO
056066     ADD     1                   TO      AI1.
056068
056070 120-S-SORTEAR.
056072     EXIT.
